-- The article-card component renders one article preview. It has no source of
-- its own — the parent (a list screen) iterates a query and hands each row in
-- via the typed `article` input. Pure presentation lives in article-card.htmlx.

##component
#article-card
    template: 'article-card.htmlx'
    styles:   ['article-card.css']

    inputs:
        article: Article
